<br>
Greater Shielding: level 34 HP/AC/Magic resist buff<br>
Steelskin: level 34 &quot;rune&quot; spell<br>
OKeil's Flickering Flame: level 34 short-duration, 5-point damage shield with +10 fire resist.<br>
Fire Elemental Aura: Increase Damage Shield by 3 (L1) to 67 (L65), Increase Fire Resist by 5<br>
<br>
Garrison's Mighty Mana Shock: Level 20 Magic-based DD (Max 148) <br>
Bonds of Force: Level 29 area effect snare (duration 1.5 minutes)<br>
Elnerick's Entombment of Ice: level 39.  Max 355 points damage with 24 second max root.<br>
Ice Shock: Level 34 ice-based DD (max 318) <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>58 fire cast: <br>
Arch shielding, Diamondskin, O'Kiels FLickering flame on self. <br>
